Description: External extensions for IvorySQL @IVORY_MAJOR@ / PostgreSQL @PG_MAJOR@
 This package adds the 29 extension controls and wal2json output plugin that
 are present in the official IvorySQL @IVORY_VERSION@ bundle but absent from
 Pigsty's IvorySQL kernel package. All PostgreSQL modules are compiled against
 /usr/ivory-@PG_MAJOR@ and use normal distribution packages for external
 runtime libraries.
